### Conclusion
Ericpiton/xai v.1.61 achieves indefinite runtime post-boot with 53W TEG output exceeding all load demands (27.5W–47W), ensuring self-sufficiency and off-grid operation. Stability is maintained with controlled temps (ferrofluid ≤85°C, CPU/GPU ≤80°C) and robust components. Feasibility is proven with current, accessible tech, making it a practical modern computer design.
